In the mean tym, 1 travellit with Sir James, that he suld pay the yeiris dewtie to his father3 andis Jhon Murray determined the questioun on his syd, this money suld be repayit be his brother to him ; quhairvnto be yieldit About the 20 oi Julj, Jhon Murrayis answcr retumit‚ declar· ing that Sir James suld pay the yeiris dewtie to his father.
